Important information

Safety Information:

Keep out of children's reach.

Ingredients:

TCP Liquid Antiseptic is a Clear Yellow Solution of Halogenated Phenols 0.68% w/v and Phenol 0.175% w/v It also contains: Glycerol, Concentrated Phosphoric Acid, E104 (Quinoline Yellow), Water

Directions:

To gargle dilute with water. Relief of Sore Throat Symptoms including those associated with Colds and Flu. Do not use if you have an allergic skin condition or are sensitive to the active ingredients. If you swallow large amounts, drink plenty of water. If still unwell see your doctor. In normal use you should not suffer unwanted side effects. However, if you notice anything unusual, talk to your doctor/pharmacist. Seek medical advice if symptoms persist for more than a few days. Simply gargle twice a day with TCP diluted with 5 parts water. DO NOT SWALLOW. Mouth Ulcers. To ease the discomfort of common mouth ulcers, dab undiluted three times a day. Should symptoms persist for more than fourteen days, consult your doctor or dentist. Cuts, Grazes, Bites, Stings. Dilute with an equal quantity of water and apply freely. In emergencies may be used undiluted. Boils, Spots, Pimples. Dab lightly, undiluted, every four hours and do not cover. Do not use after expiry date.

Product description

Product Description

TCP Liquid Antiseptic dual action which soothes pain, fights infection for sore throats, mouth ulcers, cuts, grazes, bites, stings and spots. Warnings: seek medical advice if symptoms persist for more than a few days. Keep out of reach of children. Do not use after the 'expiry date'.

To gargle, dilute with water.

Relief of sore throat symptoms including those associated with colds and flu: simply gargle twice a day with TCP diluted with five parts water. Do not swallow.

Mouth ulcers: to ease the discomfort of common mouth ulcers, dab undiluted three times a day. Should symptoms persist for more than 14 days, consult your doctor or dentist.

Cuts, grazes, bites, stings: dilute with an equal quantity of water and apply freely. In emergencies may be used undiluted.

Boils, spots, pimples: dab lightly, undiluted, every four hours and do not cover.

Ingredients

TCP Liquid Antiseptic is a Clear Yellow Solution of Halogenated Phenols 0.68% w/v and Phenol 0.175% w/v It also contains: Glycerol, Concentrated Phosphoric Acid, E104 (Quinoline Yellow), Water

Directions

To gargle dilute with water. Relief of Sore Throat Symptoms including those associated with Colds and Flu. Do not use if you have an allergic skin condition or are sensitive to the active ingredients. If you swallow large amounts, drink plenty of water. If still unwell see your doctor. In normal use you should not suffer unwanted side effects. However, if you notice anything unusual, talk to your doctor/pharmacist. Seek medical advice if symptoms persist for more than a few days. Simply gargle twice a day with TCP diluted with 5 parts water. DO NOT SWALLOW. Mouth Ulcers. To ease the discomfort of common mouth ulcers, dab undiluted three times a day. Should symptoms persist for more than fourteen days, consult your doctor or dentist. Cuts, Grazes, Bites, Stings. Dilute with an equal quantity of water and apply freely. In emergencies may be used undiluted. Boils, Spots, Pimples. Dab lightly, undiluted, every four hours and do not cover. Do not use after expiry date.

From the manufacturer

TCP Antiseptic Liquid

Symptomatic relief of sore throats including those associated with colds and influenza. Common mouth ulcers, cuts, grazes, bites, stings, boils, spots and pimples.

Gargle twice a day with TCP diluted with 5 parts water. Do not swallow.

Warning: Seek medical advice if symptoms persist for more than a few days.

Keep out of the reach and sight of children.

Ingredients

TCP Liquid Antiseptic is an aqueous solution of Phenol 0.175% w/v and halogenated phenols 0.68% w/v.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings, help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.

B. Watts
5.0 out of 5 stars Pimples are long gone!
Reviewed in the United States on 16 July 2013
Size Name: 200 ml (Pack of 1)Verified Purchase
I struggled with breakouts ever since I was in college. I tried everything...and I mean everything to try and stop them but I could never find a product or combination of products to stop my pimples. That is until I found TCP by accident!

I read somewhere online about TCP and how it zaps pimples almost overnight...I had to try it. I was a little concerned since I am in America and it only ships from overseas, but I was desperate so I ordered it. I was quite surprised how quickly the shipment arrived at my home. It was a matter of 5-7 business days. Impressive!

The first thing I noticed when trying TCP for the first time was it strong odor. But it smells clean, just like any antiseptic should, so it didn't bother me at all.

After cleansing, I soak a cotton pad with TCP and gently tone my face with it, morning and evening. Using a moisturizer after TCP in the morning will get rid of most of the antiseptic smell, so don't worry about stinking up your office or classroom.

At night, after cleansing, I tone my face again with TCP and do not put any moisturizer on after. I think this lets my face breathe while it heals itself overnight.

A few days after using this product and my face is 99% clear! I still have a few bumps on my forehead, but they are tiny and I know they will be subsiding in the next few days. My face hasn't been this clear since I was in grade school. Simply incredible.

So, if you are struggling with pimples or acne, you should absolutely give TCP a try! Not only does it work miraculously, but it's dirt cheap. What do you have to lose?
